data.description: The property's location in the sought-after Saltillo School District adds considerable value for families with school-age children who prioritize quality education. With over 2800 sq ft of living space, the home offers plenty of room for comfortable living to suit the buyer's needs. This size is ideal for larger families or individuals who appreciate spacious living areas. A large back yard is a great feature for outdoor activities, gardening, or even adding amenities like a pool or playground. It provides a private and peaceful space for relaxation and recreation.The RV hook-up on the side yard is a notable advantage, especially for RV owners or those who frequently host guests with RVs. The presence of a large shop in the back is a significant bonus for individuals with hobbies, small businesses, or those in need of extra storage space. A shop provides a dedicated area for various activities and projects, allowing for organization and creativity.
